		{
			description: [
				"Welcome to &eSupremacy&r — a pack about earning power from every direction at once."
				""
				"The spine is technology: GregTech CEu, from your first bronze boiler to fusion. Wrapped around it is magic — Botania, Ars Nouveau, and Blood Magic — and standing in your way is &eMine and Slash&r, an ARPG layer that levels your character, rolls your gear, and scales every fight. Tech, magic, and combat are not separate games here; they gate each other, trade materials, and meet in the endgame."
				""
				"You are on a community server. Other players are your economy, your rivals, and your raid team. Start with the &eMain Story&r tab, punch a tree, and begin the climb."
			]
			icon: "gtceu:creative_energy"
