			title: "Death and Recovery"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5D5D000000000001"]
			description: ["Mine and Slash in five minutes: your character has a &elevel&r — kills and quest rewards raise it, and mobs scale with you. Gear drops with &erarity&r tiers from Common to Mythic, rolling random stats called affixes. Bad drops are not trash: &esalvage&r them at a salvage station for crafting materials and stat souls, then apply souls to the gear you actually wear. Talent points build toward a class identity. That is the whole loop — kill, loot, salvage, improve. The &eCampaign&r tab's Act 0 walks you through it properly; open it before your first dungeon."]
			icon: "mmorpg:stone/1"
			id: "5D5D000000000004"
			rewards: [{
				auto: "enabled"
				command: "/mine_and_slash give xp_times_lvl @p 50"
				elevate_perms: true
				icon: "minecraft:experience_bottle"
