			title: "Mine and Slash in Five Minutes"
			x: 3.0d
			y: 3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5D5D000000000001"]
			description: ["The Twilight Forest opens from the Overworld from day one — diamonds around a water pool, throw in the flower, done. That is deliberate, not an oversight. GregTech progression in this pack requires Twilight boss trophies as crafting gates, so the dimension is early-game territory with late-game consequences. Go early for the Naga and Lich; come back later for the bosses your GT tier demands."]
			icon: "twilightforest:naga_trophy"
			id: "5D5D000000000005"
			rewards: [{
				auto: "enabled"
