		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5D5D000000000001"]
			description: ["Applied Energistics 2 channels are &einfinite&r in this pack, by config. Any cable carries any number of devices; you never need dense cables for capacity, controllers for channel routing, or the channel-planning discipline other packs demand. Build your ME network for aesthetics and cable length, nothing else. If a guide or video tells you to plan channels — that advice is for a different server."]
			icon: "ae2:controller"
			id: "5D5D000000000007"
			rewards: [{
