		{
			dependencies: ["5D5D000000000001"]
			description: ["Tinkers Construct here is &etools only&r — pickaxes, mattocks, and the Smeltery, with its weapons removed and no Tinkers armor. Combat lives elsewhere by design: &eSpartan Weaponry&r for melee variety, &eIron's Spells 'n Spellbooks&r for casting, and &eMine and Slash&r affixes riding on all of it. If a Tinkers weapon recipe seems missing, it is not missing — it never existed in this pack. Build Tinkers for the best tools in the early game and look to the combat mods for your damage."]
			icon: "tconstruct:pickaxe"
			id: "5D5D000000000008"
