		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5D5D000000000001"]
			description: ["Guns are the pack's &elate-game&r weapon class — the Gun Smith Table is gated behind Botania terrasteel, and every firearm recipe demands high-tier GregTech components, HV and beyond. There is no early musket and there will not be one. This is deliberate pacing: melee and spells carry the early and mid game, and flat-damage firearms arrive when boss health pools start demanding them. The full doctrine, tier ladder, and drop-only arsenals are documented in the &eArmory&r chapter under the Adventure tab."]
			icon: {
