		{
			dependencies: ["5D5D000000000001"]
			description: ["Shared world, simple rules. &eClaim&r your land with FTB Chunks before you build — claims are protection, not decoration. Do not grief, do not loot other players' unclaimed builds, and leave public farms as stocked as you found them. Trade through &eLightman's&r shops rather than honor-system chests; the blocks enforce fairness so nobody has to. The Commerce chapter under Home Sweet Home covers coins, shops, and the trading network. A good neighbor with a good shop is worth more than any drop in this pack."]
			icon: "lightmanscurrency:coin_gold"
